headline: Energy Transition Meets Emerging Tech on August 20th at EnerCom's 30th Anniversary Energy Investment Conference
summary: EnerCom, Inc., a leading energy consulting and strategic communications firm, announces the lineup of presenting companies for its Energy Transition and Emerging Technology Session on Wednesday, August 20, the final day of the 2025 EnerCom Denver Conference.

headline: APA Corporation Stock: Analyst Estimates & Ratings
summary: As APA Corporation has lagged behind the broader market over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a cautious outlook on the stock’s prospects.
